episodes.title: J.Y. Park Allegedly A Cult Leader?
episodes.description:
J.Y. Park is quite liked by the public for his hilarious and outrageous performances and talent for writing amazing songs. However, there is a dark side to him that people cannot dismiss. And it's his affiliation with the cult and promoting it.
